Package de.oth.blocklib

Class Context

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.Context
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClientContext, ServerContext, SinglePlayerContext
public abstract class Context
extends java.lang.Object
A Singleton that stores references to important "managing" objects. This is an alternative to a collection of multiple Singletons. The advantage is that alternative implementations of the used objects can be created by deriving from them and giving the Context the new reference.
Author:
Tobias Mueller
